<h1 style="font-size: 24px; font-weight: 600; color: #dc2626; margin: 0 0 15px 0;">Payment Failed</h1>

<p style="color: #374151; font-size: 16px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">
  Hi <%= @user.email_address.split('@').first %>,
  <br><br>
  We couldn't process the payment for your scheduled order.
</p>

<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%" style="background-color: #fef2f2; border: 1px solid #ef4444; border-radius: 8px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
  <tr>
    <td style="padding: 15px;">
      <p style="color: #991b1b; margin: 0;"><strong>Error:</strong> <%= @error_message %></p>
    </td>
  </tr>
</table>

<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%" style="background-color: #f9fafb; border-radius: 8px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
  <tr>
    <td style="padding: 15px;">
      <p style="font-weight: 600; color: #111827; margin: 0 0 10px 0;">How to fix this:</p>
      <ol style="margin: 0; padding-left: 20px; color: #374151;">
        <li style="margin-bottom: 5px;">Check that your payment method has sufficient funds</li>
        <li style="margin-bottom: 5px;">Verify your card details are up to date</li>
        <li>Click the button below to update your payment method or try again</li>
      </ol>
    </td>
  </tr>
</table>

<p style="text-align: center; margin: 25px 0;">
  <a href="<%= @retry_url %>" target="_blank" style="display: inline-block; background-color: #76e9bf; color: #000000; padding: 12px 30px; border-radius: 8px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 500;">
    Retry Payment
  </a>
</p>

<p style="color: #6b7280; font-size: 13px; margin: 0; text-align: center;">
  Your order will remain pending until you successfully complete payment.
  <br>
  If the payment isn't processed by <%= @pending_order.scheduled_for.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %>, the order will expire.
</p>
